  "title": "Competitive gymnastics WAG coach",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>WAG Competitive Coach</strong> to the\ncompetitive levels 5 & 6. </p><p>Minimum 5 years of coaching experience\nWe are looking for a coach with these qualities:</p><p>-        Passion for gymnastics and the gymnasts</p><p>-        Passion to learn and upgrade skills to improve on coaching techniques.</p><p>-        Minimum WAG FIG coaching Certification or its equivalent.</p><p>-        Ex-gymnast</p><p>-        Able to communicate well in English, written and spoken</p><p>            Prime Gymnastics club is a not-for-profit organization for over 38 years. We support the Singapore National program. </p><p>We have over 700 gymnasts participating in our developmental classes to our competitive\nlevels at FIG levels. </p><p>Interested parties, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:manager@primegym.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">manager@primegym.com</a> with your CV/Resume and Coaching\ncertificates.   </p><p> A more comprehensive job description will follow.</p><p><strong>Our ratio of Gymnasts to Coach 8 to1. Average coaching hours of 30 p/week. Admin hours 10 hours p/week.</strong></p>",
